{
  "message": "deps: add @react-three/postprocessing for 3D visual effects\n\nAdd @react-three/postprocessing v3.0.4 and postprocessing v6.38.2 to\nenable advanced post-processing effects in React Three Fiber scenes.\n\nThese packages provide:\n- Bloom effect for glowing elements\n- Noise effect for subtle film grain\n- Vignette effect for cinematic framing\n- EffectComposer for compositing multiple effects\n\nUsed in the overprompting article's constraint visualization to create\na more immersive 3D experience with proper lighting effects.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
